Package: gRaphene
Type: Package
Title: Tools for analysis of Raman data
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Emil", "Bjerglund Pedersen", "emilbp@inano.au.dk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A set of functions for analysis of Raman spectroscopy data from Renishaw Wire.
  Contains tools for loading, modifying and plotting both individual spectra, curve fit results
  and spatial maps.
